eading-150"><div class="inline pr-4 text-17 font-bold md:text-17">Sharge’s newest sci-fi power banks look pretty sweet in person.</div><p class="duet--article--dangerously-set-cms-markup inline font-fkroman text-gray-33 dark:text-gray-ef [&amp;_a]:relative [&amp;_a]:z-10   [&amp;_a:hover]:shadow-highlight-franklin [&amp;_a]:text-gray-33 [&amp;_a]:shadow-underline-gray-33 dark:[&amp;_a]:text-gray-ef dark:[&amp;_a]:shadow-underline-franklin"><a href="/2023/10/6/23906552/sharge-sharegeek-storm-retro-mac-sale-best-price">I’m a sucker for Sharge’s charging gear</a> because it looks like nothing else, and that continues to be true of the new Sharge 170 model and especially the “Internet Hostkey” in my CES hands-on gallery below. Be warned that<a href="https://sharge.com/products/internet-hostkey"> the Hostkey</a> comes in a wimpy 40Wh capacity model in addition to its reasonable 72Wh one. <a href="https://www.instagram.com/reel/CwS0v9mJApy/">Here’s my video with a few earlier Sharge products</a>.</p><br/></div><div class="pt-12"><section tabindex="-1" aria-label=" carousel" class="duet--article--gallery relative overflow-hidden outline-none my-10 w-full"><div class="relative mb-10 h-[238px] bg-gray-ef md:h-[400px]"><span style="box-sizing:border-box;display:block;overflow:hidden;width:initial;height:initial;background:none;opacity:1;border:0;margin:0;padding:0;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;bottom:0;right:0"><img alt="&lt;em&gt;The $119 Sharge 170 is bigger and more powerful than its predecessors — with a nicer screen, too.&lt;/em&gt;" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAAAAAP///yH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAIBRAA7" decoding="async" data-nimg="fill" class="relative top-1/2 mx-auto max-h-full max-w-full visible" style="position:absolute;top:0;left:0;bottom:0;right:0;box-sizing:border-box;padding:0;border:none;margin:auto;display:block;width:0;height:0;min-width:100%;max-width:100%;min-height:100%;max-height:100%;object-fit:contain"/><noscript><img alt="&lt;em&gt;The $119 Sharge 170 is bigger and more powerful than its predecessors — with a nicer screen, too.&lt;/em&gt;" loading="lazy" decoding="async" data-nimg="fill" style="position:absolute;top:0;left:0;bottom:0;right:0;box-sizing:border-box;padding:0;border:none;margin:auto;display:block;width:0;height:0;min-width:100%;max-width:100%;min-height:100%;max-height:100%;object-fit:contain" class="relative top-1/2 mx-auto max-h-full max-w-full visible" sizes="(max-width: 1023px) 100vw, 744px" srcSet="https://duet-cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/0x0:2040x1530/376x282/filters:focal(1020x765:1021x766):format(webp)/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_asset/file/25210857/ces_unveiled_010.jpg 376w, https://duet-cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/0x0:2040x1530/384x288/filters:focal(1020x765:1021x766):format(webp)/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_asset/file/25210857/ces_unveiled_010.jpg 384w, https://duet-cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/0x0:2040x1530/415x311/filters:focal(1020x765:1021x766):format(webp)/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_asset/file/25210857/ces_unveiled_010.jpg 415w, https://duet-cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/0x0:2040x1530/480x360/filters:focal(1020x765:1021x766):format(webp)/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_asset/file/25210857/ces_unveiled_010.jpg 480w, https://duet-cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/0x0:2040x1530/540x405/filters:focal(1020x765:1021x766):format(webp)/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_asset/file/25210857/ces_unveiled_010.jpg 540w, https://duet-cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/0x0:2040x1530/640x480/filters:focal(1020x765:1021x766):format(webp)/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_asset/file/25210857/ces_unveiled_010.jpg 640w, https://duet-cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/0x0:2040x1530/750x563/filters:focal(1020x765:1021x766):format(webp)/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_asset/file/25210857/ces_unveiled_010.jpg 750w, https://duet-cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/0x0:2040x1530/828x621/filters:focal(1020x765:1021x766):format(webp)/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_asset/file/25210857/ces_unveiled_010.jpg 828w, https://duet-cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/0x0:2040x15